metadata.name: Sampic Vintage 1/1
metadata.description:
Out into the boroughs, neo-Renaissance style, with American textile industry decorative mementos. A strategic maneuver for market distribution. The movement of materials and clothing, in and out, of high-rise factories and low slung streets. Design, cut and sell. Oversized neon orange drawstring hoodie, floral velour bomber jacket, frayed hem dark wash skirt, black cotton thigh high stockings. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model wearing a detailed red floral printed purple and red puffy jacket, with a ripped denim miniskirt, black high top sneakers, bright orange socks, blue hair, red lipstick, walking down manhattan in the 2000s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
